### Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1

### Search Product by Code (BST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search/code/WC001

### Get Sorted Products (BST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/sorted

### Get Recent Items (Linked List)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/recent

### Get Low Stock Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/low-stock

### Get Restock Requests (Queue)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/restock-requests

### Advanced Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/search
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "searchTerm": "Buddha",
  "category": "Statues",
  "woodType": "Teak",
  "minPrice": 10000.00,
  "maxPrice": 20000.00,
  "minStock": 5
}

### Stock Prediction
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/predict-stock/WC001?days=30

### Product Recommendations
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/recommend/WC001?maxRecommendations=5

### Record Stock Consumption
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/record-consumption/WC001?quantityConsumed=5

### ============================================
### PURCHASE ORDER MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### Create Purchase Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase-orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "supplierId": 1,
  "orderDate": "2025-01-17T10:00:00",
  "expectedDeliveryDate": "2025-01-24T10:00:00",
  "notes": "Urgent order",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 50,
      "unitPrice": 10000.00
    }
  ]
}

### Get All Purchase Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase-orders

### Get Purchase Order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase-orders/1

### ============================================
### GRN MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### Create GRN
POST {{baseUrl}}/grns
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "purchaseOrderId": 1,
  "receivedDate": "2025-01-17T10:00:00",
  "notes": "All items received",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "orderedQuantity": 50,
      "receivedQuantity": 50,
      "unitPrice": 10000.00
    }
  ]
}

### Get All GRNs
GET {{baseUrl}}/grns

### Get GRN by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/grns/1

### Complete GRN (Updates Stock)
POST {{baseUrl}}/grns/1/complete

### Get GRNs by Purchase Order
GET {{baseUrl}}/grns/purchase-order/1

