### SALES ORDER MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### Create Sales Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales-orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "orderDate": "2025-01-17T10:00:00",
  "expectedDeliveryDate": "2025-01-20T10:00:00",
