### ============================================
### INVOICE MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### Create Invoice from Sales Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/from-sales-order/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "invoiceDate": "2025-01-17T10:00:00",
  "dueDate": "2025-02-17T10:00:00",
  "notes": "Payment terms: 30 days"
}

### Get All Invoices
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices

### Get Invoice by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/1

### Issue Invoice
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/1/issue

### Record Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/1/payment?paymentAmount=5000.00

### Get Invoices by Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/customer/1

### Get Invoices by Sales Order
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/sales-order/1

